title: First proposal for #586 Hexagonal Architecture primary ports should have interfaces
body:
It's a first proposal add interface primary ports for this issue #586.

I have adapted the ConsoleLottery with LotteryService Interface and implemented this. The ConsoleLottery create a new instance of LotteryServiceImpl and move this logic in the LotteryServiceImpl.

Maybe it's not a the best name for this class, but if you like the implementation, I will adapt the names of the classes and do the same with ConsoleAdministration.

@iluwatar Do you like this adaptation for Hexagonal Architecture with interface?

title: Dependency 'junit-platform-launcher' is added
body:
The AppTest class in factory pattern has an error because of junit-platform-launcher' eclipse bug on version **Oxygen.3 Release (4.7.3)**. 

Dependency '**junit-platform-launcher**' is added to pom.xml for running test classes.

For detail info about Eclipse bug, please [click here.](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/46717693/eclipse-no-tests-found-using-junit-5-caused-by-noclassdeffounderror)

title: Trampoline pattern logger fix
body:
Trampoline pattern has logger object build error.
The error fixed with using **org.slf4j.Logger**.

Instead of using anatation, Logger object is created for logging.
